OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,FA "dangerous, conniving" stalker who
OL,7,Fdeliberately drove into his ex-wife
OL,8,Fbefore attacking her with a baseball
OL,9,Fbat has been jailed.
OL,11,FCCTV footage showed Laurance Worvill,
OL,12,F51, colliding with the woman as she
OL,13,Fwalked on the pavement outside a cafe
OL,14,Fon Chanterlands Avenue in Hull in May
OL,15,F2025.
OL,17,FHe then got out of the car and
OL,18,Frepeatedly hit her with the bat before
OL,19,Fwitnesses intervened.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,FThe woman suffered head and leg
OL,7,Finjuries and a broken finger.
OL,9,FWorvill, of Spring Bank West in Hull,
OL,10,Fhad broken into a Royal Mail office
OL,11,Fthe day before the incident to try to
OL,12,Ffind letters showing where the victim
OL,13,Flived.
OL,15,FHe was found guilty of attempted
OL,16,Fmurder after a trial and was jailed
OL,17,Ffor 24 years with an extended four-
OL,18,Fyear licence period.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentencing, the
OL,7,Fwoman said: "I never thought I would
OL,8,Fbe put in this position, or that
OL,9,Fsomething like this would ever happen
OL,10,Fto me.
OL,12,F"Without the heroic actions of those
OL,13,Fwho came to my aid that day, it would
OL,14,Fhave been a very different outcome. I
OL,15,Fhave no doubt that they saved my life."
OL,17,FHull Crown Court heard the woman was
OL,18,Ftrapped against railings when she was
OL,19,Fdriven into by Worvill on 7 May last
OL,20,Fyear.
OL,26,@oD@MOUtD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,FHe shouted that he wanted to kill her
OL,7,Fas he beat her with the bat.
OL,9,FThe judge John Thackray KC told
OL,10,FWorvill he had shown "not a jot of
OL,11,Fremorse" and had the "temerity" to try
OL,12,Fto justify his attack by claiming his
OL,13,Fex-wife had failed to feed his koi
OL,14,Fcarp.
OL,16,FThe woman appealed to other victims of
OL,17,Fdomestic abuse to "reach out and talk
OL,18,Fto someone".
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,F"Whether that's a trusted friend, or
OL,7,Ffamily member, the police, charity or
OL,8,Fsupport agency, please tell someone,"
OL,9,Fshe said.
OL,11,F"I wish I had done it sooner, but now
OL,12,FI am overwhelmed with the result and
OL,13,Fthat Worvill is finally behind bars
OL,14,Fwhere he belongs."
OL,16,FDet Insp Helen Collier, of Humberside
OL,17,FPolice, described Worvill as a "cruel
OL,18,Fand calculating" man who had an
OL,19,F"obsession" with his ex-wife.
OL,26,@vD@RO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,FShe added: "Worvill is a dangerous,
OL,7,Fconniving individual who subjected a
OL,8,Fwoman to an unimaginable attack which
OL,9,Fleft her spending ten days in hospital.
OL,11,F"I am pleased Worvill will be behind
OL,12,Fbars for a very long time, but by no
OL,13,Fmeans does the result today take away
OL,14,Fthe trauma and pain the woman will
OL,15,Fcontinue to face on a daily basis as
OL,16,Fshe tries to navigate through life on
OL,17,Fwhat will be a long journey of
OL,18,Fphysical and emotional recovery."
OL,26,@nD@LOUsD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
