FL,333,330,260,120,000,100
PN,33207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F332A1783685998
OL,3,CMan who attacked ex-wife with car and
OL,4,Cbaseball bat jailed
OL,6,FAs well as attempted murder, Worvill
OL,7,Fhad admitted burglary, possession of
OL,8,Fan offensive weapon, disqualified
OL,9,Fdriving and breaching a restraining
OL,10,Forder.
OL,12,FHe was given an indefinite restraining
OL,13,Forder.
OL,15,FPolice said proceeds from the sale of
OL,16,Fthe car, which was seized, will go to
OL,17,Fthe owner of the coffee shop damaged
OL,18,Fin the incident.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/7
